1. **No usePoints hook** - Extract domain has no dedicated hook (pointsBalance exists in store but no hook wrapper)
2. **No useMarketplace hook** - Marketplace domain has no hook
3. **No useProducts hook** - Products domain has no hook  
4. **No useParameter hook** - Parameter domain has no hook
5. **No useExtract hook** - Extract domain has no hook for main transactions

---

